## PGE Issue Labeling

Every issue must have all three required label categories:

| Category | Labels |
|----------|--------|
| **Type** | `pge/type:prd` or `pge/type:change` |
| **Scope** | `pge/scope:[your-scope]` — add all affected scopes |
| **Status** | `pge/status:triage` (always start here) |

